The '''Capobastone''' is a high-ranking [['Ndrangheta]] who is in charge of a [['ndrina]].<ref>{{Cite web|title=The 'Ndrangheta Looms Large |url=http://americanmafia.com/Feature_Articles_286.html |website=americanmafia.com |access-date=2016-02-10 |last=La Sorte |first=Mike |date=December 2004 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304054929/http://americanmafia.com/Feature_Articles_286.html |archivedate=2016-03-04 |df= }}</ref> It is the [[Calabria]]n equivalent for the [[Sicily|Sicilian]] "[[Boss (crime)|Capofamiglia]]".
==Rule== In a 'ndrina, the Capobastone make the most important decisions, and report only at the "[[Capo crimine]]", the head of the "[[Crimine]]". Sometimes he can take the control of all 'Ndrangheta, but he has to be elected by the various Capibastone.
